commit.message:
dsp16xx-protos.h, [...]: Replace "GNU CC" with "GCC".

	* config/dsp16xx/dsp16xx-protos.h, config/dsp16xx/dsp16xx.c,
	config/dsp16xx/dsp16xx.h, config/dsp16xx/dsp16xx.md: Replace
	"GNU CC" with "GCC".

From-SVN: r64301
